Product name: MOLLIE - Nude colour lace Bridesmaid Shift Dress - Nude matt duchess satin and peach lace - Size small - Size 10 - simple bridesmaid dress
Description:
Hello!
I‚Äôm Anna, a designer and dressmaker based near Brighton in the UK. I design and make every dress here in my home studio at the seaside for my bridal wear label; ‚ÄòThis Modern Love‚Äô. 
About This Modern Love
The aesthetic for ‚ÄòThis Modern Love‚Äô is romantic, feminine, bohemian and beautifully simple dresses, all hand crafted using the finest materials such as silk chiffon, corded lace, duchess satin and soft tulle.  My dresses are designed in a delicate colour palette including of ivory, nude and blush tones, though lots more colours are available.
All of my dresses are a relaxed, pull on style which cinch in at the waist with elastic - they are not structured or fitted. Because of this, my designs feel comfortable, lightweight and fluid. My customers are often women looking for a relaxed, vintage style or bohemian dress, with a woodland, rustic or festival theme to their wedding: brides looking for something simple, beautiful and original.
Highlights for This Modern Love
Named as ‚ÄòThe One to Watch‚Äô in Perfect Wedding Magazine (Apr 2016)
Finalist at the UK Wedding Awards for Best Bridesmaid Collection 2016 (You and Your Wedding & Hitched.co.uk) (Jan 2016)
Featured in Elle Magazine, Vogue Italia, Style and The Bride, The Bohemian Wedding, Hochzeitswahn, The Wedding Bazaar, Bespoke Bride, Love Sussex Weddings,  Save The Date, Love Our Wedding, Oh Comely, Little Book for Brides and Etsy‚Äôs Editor Picks.
Winner of the Elle Magazine & Warehouse Talent Spot 2013
Featured supplier at the Etsy Wedding Fair (London, June 2015)
About this dress
MOLLIE BRIDESMAID DRESS
A pretty and elegant bridesmaid dress. Made in a nude coloured matt duchess satin, the top of the dress has a layer of pretty peach/blush coloured lace and little scallop edge cap sleeves. Finished with a pretty grosgrain ribbon tied at the waist.
Simple and beautiful. Perfect for a relaxed, modern wedding. Ideal as bridesmaid or flower girl dress.
(Model is 5ft 11 and sz 10)
Only one dress available.
A scoop neck design at the front and the back of the dress (the back scoop is slightly higher than the front).
Like all This Modern Love dresses, this design is a simple, unstructured pull on design. It simply pulls on over the head and cinches at the waist with elastic, there are no fastenings, zips etc. The design is relaxed and non fitted. 
Ready to wear dresses
This listing is for the dress pictured in the photographs, it‚Äôs a ‚Äòready to wear‚Äô dress which means that the dress is the size listed only. This style is not currently available as a ‚Äòmade to order/bespoke‚Äô dress as the fabric used to create it is no longer available.
Want to try it on? That‚Äôs absolutely fine! You‚Äôre welcome to order the dress to try it and if it‚Äôs not suitable then you can return the dress for a full refund. Returns must be notified within a strict 7 day period of the receipt of the dress. I‚Äôm sorry, but postage costs are non refundable. If you‚Äôd like more information, measurements or photos of the dress to check whether it will be suitable then please let me know and I will be happy to assist.
Can I visit your studio?
Yes! I have a home studio which you are welcome to visit to try on the dresses. Please contact me to make an appointment. I‚Äôm based on the regency parade on Worthing seafront which is approximately 20 minutes from Brighton (UK). Studio details provided upon request.
Like to know more?
You can read more about my designs, highlights, background, FAQs and testimonials from real brides on my website & take a look at my portfolio of work on my social media too on Wordpress, Pinterest, Facebook, Instagram & Twitter.

All jewelry is hand stamped. Hand stamping is a method which involves each letter, design, punctuation etc being stamped by hand using a brass mallet against stainless steel block.
It is often confused with engraving or machine imprinted but that is far from the case!
